description:
High.Energy.Metal.233.songs.Collection.by.Z3

This collection reflects my taste when it comes to heavy rock music. I like metal with energy and kick, speed is less important but it sure helps. The selection is fairly narrow, If you&#039;re reading this because you like some of these the songs, chances are will find some new stuff you like (internet is great that way!).
If you want to preview it or listen while downloadning, go to http://xfactor.mosen.nu.
The stream has been playing music like this 24/7 for almost 4 years, this is how the playlist looked 2008-11-09.

Again, this reflects MY taste. If you&#039;re gonna comment about it, atleast try be constructive. Dont just whine and complain about the selection, noone is forcing you to download anything!
I&#039;m always on the lookout for more music like this, and im sure im not alone. Give suggestions on music like this ... I want more!! Comments like "OMG WTF Marilun Manson SUXXX!!" or "Slipknot Is teh bestest, FUCK ALL ELSE!!" will only reveal you like a 12 year old inbreed with pimples ... dont bother, noone cares.

Finally, dont narrow yourself to this genre. Makes sure you listen to other stuff as well, from the old champions like Pink Floyd, Beatles, Jimi Hendrix and Led Zeppelin to music from contemporary artists.
Form your own opinion, dont let prejudice guide you ... keep an open mind!!
